35:28.705 --> 35:30.740
No, no one does.

35:30.773 --> 35:32.274
Oh.

35:32.307 --> 35:34.243
You are delightful.

35:38.080 --> 35:42.150
♪ Lady, let me love you ♪

35:42.184 --> 35:46.154
